{"tid":94162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"摸14歲援交女胸並接受口交     內向修理員判服務令","createTime":"2017-01-25T04:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T06:00:48.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53ff783ff24de6473bd0c1a18929f2e3141f365d","tid":94162,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170125/large/1485316831_19c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170125%2Flarge%2F1485316831_19c4.jpg&h=eb117173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n25歲電子修理員自稱在損友建議下，透過Instagram認識14歲樣子成熟的援交少女，對方同意以1,500元讓修理員親吻擁抱及替他口交，最後修理員在少女的寓所摸少女的胸及下體，少女替他口交。修理員早前在裁判法院承認4項罪名，裁判官今指被告符合社會服務令條件，而且已還柙6星期，相信已收阻嚇作用，故判被告接受120小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n修理員張國裕(25歲)早前承認非禮及向16歲以下兒童作猥褻行為罪共4罪。辯方求情指，從無拍拖經驗的被告過往曾三度被異性拒絕追求，被告性格內向，事件中女童亦有向被告索取金錢，被告承認犯案非常愚蠢，不明白案件嚴重性，對事件有悔意，律師形容被告性本善，要求輕判。"},{"pid":"d019a721cc0f448bc48241f0829d0e018c944638","tid":94162,"uid":58228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"女人無敵"},{"pid":"84b42ffbdb9126cdab0e7ea2d20efa68e3ba9978","tid":94162,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人無敵</blockquote><br />\n錢就照袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781fdf9b80df4cf1322f8b9cb7ea51749873a98a","tid":94162,"uid":47135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女人無敵</blockquote><br />\n錢就照袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公平咩"},{"pid":"f8a64cad0471837a7182b78e839ed93a845223dc","tid":94162,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:20:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f4ad03b3b317bae6666f546aa2a23f18d813a16","tid":94162,"uid":64283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":